Answer - 



Message - 


QAndA - 

To find all Questions asked by a particular Customer : 

Select Question.* , User.FirstName, User.LastName, User.Photograph from QAndA Natural Join Question, User where CustomerUserID = MyUserID and QAndA.ServiceProviderUserID = User.UserID;

To find answers to a Question :

Select * from Answer where QuestionID = MyQuestionID;


Wishlist -

Select Wish.*, Service.*, Region.* from Wish, Service, Location where Wish.CustomerUserID = MyUserID;

Select Bids.* from Bids, User where Customer.UserID= MyUserID and WishId = MyWishId and Bids.ServiceProviderUSerID = User.UserID;


Appointments -

Select * from Appointment where CustomerUserID = MyUserID;

ServiceProviderUserID - 

Friends -

Select User.FirstName, User.LastName, User.EmailID, User.Photograph, User.ContactNumber from Follows, User where Follows.FollowerCustomerUserID = MyUserID and Follows.FollowedCustomerUserID = User.UserID;



For Service Provider - 

To find all Questions asked to a particular Service Provider : 

Select Question.* , User.FirstName, User.LastName, User.Photograph from QAndA Natural Join Question, User where ServiceProviderUserID = MyUserID and QAndA.CustomerUserID = User.UserID;


Appointments -

Select * from Appointment where ServiceProviderUserID = MyUserID;

Bids ;

Select Wish.*, Service.*, Region.*, Bid.* from Wish, Service, Location, Bid where Bid.ServiceProviderUserID = MyUserID and Wish.CustomerUserID = Bid.CustomerUserID;

